&gt;&gt; Hi, I actually work at the
Library of Congress and we go

00:08:57.660 --> 00:08:59.050
to Good Stuff and my co-worker
go to Good Stuff and We,

00:08:59.870 --> 00:08:59.900
the Pizza almost everyday
or twice a week--

00:09:02.640 --> 00:09:04.440
&gt;&gt; We, The Pizza, have you
guys heard about We, The Pizza?

00:09:04.640 --> 00:09:05.640
Yeah? No? Okay.

